Text:
MTI Home Video (US DVD), Lighthouse DVD Distribution (UK DVD) 
Cast 

Jesse Jane, Carmen Luvana, Janine, Teagan Presley, Devon, Austyn Moore, Jenaveve Jolie, Tommy Gunn, Evan Stone 

Plot :  
The movie tells the tale of the rescue of Manuel Valenzuela who had been kidnapped by the evil pirate Victor Stagnetti. Isabella, Manuel's new bride, is thrown overboard. She is later found and taken aboard the Sea Stallion. The captain, Edward Reynolds, dreams to one day become a great pirate hunter and his first mate Jules convinces him to track down Stagnetti.
